title: (Fri Full) Kathie Lee Gifford In-Studio Sharing Celebrity Stories + Kameron Marlowe on Going From Selling Car Parts to Being on The Voice   + The Story of Garth Brooks Alter Ego
itunes:title: (Fri Full) Kathie Lee Gifford In-Studio Sharing Celebrity Stories + Kameron Marlowe on Going From Selling Car Parts to Being on The Voice   + The Story of Garth Brooks Alter Ego
description:
Kathie Lee Gifford stops by to talk about her new movie and book. She also shares some great stories about celebrities she’s encountered over her career in television and entertainment. New artist Kameron Marlowe stops by to talk about his new album, being on The Voice and getting to play a cool show in his hometown.  Bobby received a voicemail from a listener who had no idea Garth Brooks had an alter ego in the 90s! Bobby and Eddie share the story of Chris Gaines.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
